<h2>CNV-Aware Epigenomic Modeling Framework</h2>
<p>
Designed and implemented a negative binomial generalized additive model (GAM-NB)
for copy number–aware epigenomic analysis. The framework integrates GC content
and mappability covariates to improve segmentation accuracy, reduce bias,
and enhance downstream peak detection and regulatory interpretation.
